A night of love, elegance, and unforgettable moments at the iconic Detroit Athletic Club! 💍

From a breathtaking ceremony at Holy Cross Greek Orthodox Church to a Korean wedding ceremony during their reception, Rachel & Michael’s wedding was a seamless blend of tradition, romance, and timeless celebration. 

📍 Detroit weddings always bring a magical energy—city lights, historic venues, and that unbeatable Motor City charm. This day was nothing short of EPIC!
